We’re with you every step of the way.
Learn more about our services for individual investors and families.



1
Discovery
We want to know what makes you tick. We want to know what’s important to you – not just where your money is. So we take time to get to know you, your hopes and dreams, your relationships, your businesses and your hobbies. And once we know where you stand today, we build a plan to help you get where you want to be tomorrow.

 

2
Planning
A centerpiece of the Buckingham experience is the development of a thoughtful, customized financial plan designed to help you achieve your most important goals. Your plan gives you the confidence to weather the ups and downs of the market and freedom to focus on the things in life that matter most to you.

 

3
Implementation
With the right plan in place, we stay with you. We keep an eye on your assets, so you can keep your eye on your life. We keep you updated on how you’re doing, because we believe you can sleep better at night when you know someone’s watching out for you.





We understand the importance of the trusted position you hold.
Learn more about our financial services for institutions.



1
Discovery
The first step in the Buckingham experience is to get to know your organization’s mission. We look at your needs, your goals, your assets – and then pinpoint ways we can help. Ways we can help strengthen your connection to your donors and supporters. Ways we can partner with you to enable your organization to continue doing its important work.   

 

2
Planning
As your strategic investment partner, we create an evidence-based investment plan that takes into account your organization’s need, ability and willingness to take risk. Every recommendation we make is based on an objective fiduciary promise – so you know with confidence how we’re acting in your organization’s best interests at all times.

 

3
Implementation
We’re with you every step of the way. We provide long-term services, support and ongoing education for your fellow board members and constituents. We are here to support your organization’s mission and strengthen its ability to achieve it now and for generations to come.





Improving the odds of a successful retirement.
Learn more about our retirement plan solutions.



1
Discovery
We start by getting to know your company, your goals, and your existing plan. We then work with you to create or redesign a retirement solution that can maximize participation and contributions, and increase the odds of your employees successfully funding their retirement. We take our fiduciary responsibility to heart, always acting in your best interests.

 

2
Education
As we start managing your 401(k) plan, we help each of your participating employees find the ideal savings rate and the right investment mix for their individual situation. Our experience shows this additional level of advice increases savings – and helps employees feel better about their plan.

 

3
Implementation
Our evidence-based investment philosophy means we make recommendations based on what the science of investing has shown to be most effective, not the latest Wall Street speculation. This approach helps your employees stop worrying about the daily ups and downs of the market and put their focus where it should be: on their work, their careers, and their families.





We’re with you every step of the way.
Learn more about our specialized services for healthcare professionals.



1
Discovery
We want to know what makes you tick. What’s important to you – personally and professionally? What goals do you have for yourself, your career, your family, your practice? We understand the unique challenges you face – and we’re here to help you make your most important dreams come true.

 

2
Planning
You work hard – so we want to make sure you have the tools you need to achieve your goals. Our knowledgeable teams of CFP®s, CPAs and Advisors have created the Wealth Accelerator System™ to help you create a plan to make it all happen. We help you develop an understanding of where your money goes and where it should go, and create spending and savings model you can follow to give you the best chance for long-term wealth.

 

3
Implementation
With the right plan in place, we stay by your side, helping you make the right choices about buying or selling equipment, bringing on staff and transitioning your practice. We keep an eye on your personal finances, too – so you can sleep better at night knowing someone’s watching out for what’s best for you.






















 





