 Choosing a Trusted Advisor
Read more





Where the rubber meets the road.
With your plan in place, your Buckingham team then puts it into action, working with your accountant, estate planner, attorney and other advisors to ensure your money is where it should be based on your current and future needs.
Our Investment Policy Committee, a full-time team made up of advisors, researchers and financial specialists, continuously studies, evaluates, and applies the latest peer-reviewed financial research to ensure the recommendations we make live up to our exacting standards.
Our dedicated fixed income team helps you find the best ways to balance risk while providing protection against inflation. Each client’s need for fixed income assets is unique. Your Buckingham advisor will help you find and preserve the right balance for you.
Taxes, of course, are a big part of the equation, and, having been founded by four CPAs, central to our approach to wealth management. We look at taxes as a year-round strategy, monitoring your plan, your investments and the performance of the market for tax-loss harvesting opportunities.



