Buckingham Asset Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 4:41 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Buckingham Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Buckingham Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, corporations, and charitable organizations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages equity and fixed income mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It was founded in 1994 and is based in St. Louis, Missouri with additional offices in Santa Rosa, California; Park City, Utah; Cupertino, California; Burlingame, California; and Palo Alto, California. Buckingham Asset Manage...
Buckingham Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, corporations, and charitable organizations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages equity and fixed income mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It was founded in 1994 and is based in St. Louis, Missouri with additional offices in Santa Rosa, California; Park City, Utah; Cupertino, California; Burlingame, California; and Palo Alto, California. Buckingham Asset Management, LLC operates as a subsidiary of The Buckingham Family of Financial Services.
